item.title: CVE-2023-22657|2023-02-01T17:56:01.101Z -- f5 -- f5os-a
item.description: On F5OS-A beginning in version 1.2.0 to before 1.3.0 and F5OS-C beginning in version 1.3.0 to before 1.5.0, processing F5OS tenant file names may allow for command injection. Note: Software versions which have reached End of Technical Support (EoTS) are not evaluated.
